OL,3,CThe difficult decisions at Maghaberry
OL,4,CPrison as inmate numbers reach new
OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,FHundreds of inmates in previously
OL,8,Fmothballed accommodation blocks, 40%
OL,9,Fof prisoners sharing cells, and
OL,10,Fcancelled skills and education
OL,11,Fsessions - this is the current state
OL,12,Fof affairs inside Maghaberry Prison as
OL,13,Fthe population there reaches a new
OL,14,Fhigh of almost 1,500.
OL,16,FCoping with numbers that are on a
OL,17,Fconstant upward trajectory falls to
OL,18,Fthe new governor at Northern Ireland's
OL,19,Fhigh security prison.
