OL,4,CPrison as inmate numbers reach new
OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,FIn her first broadcast interview since
OL,8,Ftaking up the post permanently earlier
OL,9,Fthis year, Tracy Megrath has told UTV
OL,10,Fthat difficult decisions are being
OL,11,Fmade to keep finding the capacity for
OL,12,Fadmissions, because turning people
OL,13,Faway is "not an option".
OL,15,FThe population of 1,449 is the highest
OL,16,Fever, but management says there is
OL,17,F"still a considerable way to go"
OL,18,Fbefore reaching capacity and being
OL,19,Fconsidered "overcrowded".
