OL,3,CThe difficult decisions at Maghaberry
OL,4,CPrison as inmate numbers reach new
OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,FThe brand new #54million Davis House
OL,8,Fwas built in 2019. Several years ago,
OL,9,Ffour disused 1986 prison blocks were
OL,10,Fprepared as an emergency contingency
OL,11,Fplan to make more space, and it was
OL,12,Fhoped they would only need to be used
OL,13,Ftemporarily.
OL,15,FDuring UTV's visit, there were over
OL,16,F300 prisoners in these blocks in so-
OL,17,Fcalled 'Red Square' and only two
OL,18,Flandings were not in use - those two
OL,19,Flandings had 36 empty cells.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
