OL,3,CThe difficult decisions at Maghaberry
OL,4,CPrison as inmate numbers reach new
OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,F"If we reached capacity, we would
OL,8,Fsimply add some more doubling up
OL,9,Fspaces," said Governor Megrath.
OL,11,F"This morning, there are 558 men in
OL,12,Fcustody here who are doubled up, and
OL,13,Fthat's not ideal. But if we had to, we
OL,14,Fwould increase that number.
OL,16,F"We do risk assess everybody who
OL,17,Fdoubles up and we do everything we can
OL,18,Fto make sure that that is as easier
OL,19,Fprocess for people as possible.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
