OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,FHowever, just last week, Ulster
OL,8,FUnionist MLA Doug Beattie said
OL,9,Fwhistleblowers had told him there was
OL,10,F"tension" inside Maghaberry because
OL,11,Fthe staff to prisoner ratio meant some
OL,12,Fgym, skills and education slots were
OL,13,Fcancelled.
OL,15,FResponding to these claims, Governor
OL,16,FMegrath said: "I personally, I'm not
OL,17,Fpicking up on tension. We do have
OL,18,Fincidents, yes we do... This is an
OL,19,Foperational environment, we do have
OL,20,Fincidents, but those are generally an
OL,21,Fexception.
