OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,F"In an ideal world, we would have
OL,8,Feverybody in a single cell where I
OL,9,Fwould be able to close the older
OL,10,Faccommodation and give everybody
OL,11,Faccommodation of the standard that we
OL,12,Fhave in Davis House, where everybody
OL,13,Fin custody is free to engage in
OL,14,Factivities, and skills that allow them
OL,15,Fto move forward on release and
OL,16,Fhopefully not come back to Maghaberry."
