OL,7,FGovernor Megrath said working with
OL,8,Fother agencies within the Department
OL,9,Fof Justice could help reduce the
OL,10,Fnumbers arriving at the prison in the
OL,11,Ffirst place.
OL,13,F"I think we need to look at how long
OL,14,Fpeople spend on remand," she said.
