OL,7,F"I think we need to look at other
OL,8,Falternatives. Is there an alternative,
OL,9,Fperhaps, to look at more tagging in
OL,10,Fthe community? It's all around public
OL,11,Fsafety. That all this has to be
OL,12,Ffactored in because, public safety is
OL,13,Fkey."
OL,15,FUTV put questions about the situation
