OL,4,CPrison as inmate numbers reach new
OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,FNaomi Long said there is no sense of
OL,8,Fovercrowding, but that the service is
OL,9,F"absolutely being impacted by the
OL,10,Fnumbers" of prisoners, and the high
OL,11,Fproportion on remand.
OL,13,F"In truth, we have still very high
OL,14,Fnumbers of remand prisoners, higher
OL,15,Fthan anywhere else in these islands at
OL,16,Faround 50 per cent in Maghaberry and
OL,17,Fabout 38 or 39 per cent overall, so
OL,18,Fvery high levels and it's something
OL,19,Fthat we are we're seeking to tackle,"
OL,20,Fsaid Minister Long.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@HO]uD@AOU{D@eO]
