OL,3,CThe difficult decisions at Maghaberry
OL,4,CPrison as inmate numbers reach new
OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,F"So what we are trying to do at the
OL,8,Fmoment is work with our partners in
OL,9,Fthe justice system to look at
OL,10,Falternatives to remand. So we're
OL,11,Flooking, for example, a bail support
OL,12,Fschemes for women prisoners as a pilot.
OL,14,F"We're also trying to look at those
OL,15,Fprisoners who are on remand and who
OL,16,Fmay never actually serve a day as a
OL,17,Fsentenced prisoner.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
