OL,5,Chighs
OL,7,F"Are there ways we can expedite that
OL,8,Fthrough the system either so that they
OL,9,Fare sentenced and we can then engage
OL,10,Fwith rehabilitation, or that they are
OL,11,Freleased on bail with whatever
OL,12,Fconditions are necessary to do that.
OL,14,F"So we're looking at all of those
OL,15,Foptions."
OL,17,FThe Minister welcomed the recent
OL,18,Fpassing out of almost 70 new officers,
OL,19,Fand praised those who have already
OL,20,Fbeen working in the Prison Service.
